# StreamGraphRoller - Live Scrolling Metric Plotter

StreamGraphRoller renders clean, animated charts from fast-moving numeric streams in testing and production.

## Features
- Smooth live updates  
- Adjustable scroll speed  
- Built with Matplotlib  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/26_StreamGraphRoller.git
cd 26_StreamGraphRoller
python visualize.py
